OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMorning low cloud lifting to
OL,6,Fleave a fine day, with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine, although some cloud
OL,8,Flingering along eastern coasts. Still
OL,9,Frather windy in the southwest. Warm
OL,10,Ffor most, but remaining chilly along
OL,11,Feastern coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry night will follow with
OL,14,Fclear spells. Breezy in the southwest,
OL,15,Fbut light winds elsewhere. Mist and
OL,16,Ffog likely across central and eastern
OL,17,Fareas by morning. Feeling chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
