OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny mist, fog and low cloud in
OL,6,Fthe east will clear quickly after the
OL,7,Fsunrise. Another bright and sunny day
OL,8,Fexpected with temperatures slightly
OL,9,Fhigher than Thursday. Generally less
OL,10,Fwindy.
